    "After the video, participants were presented with a comprehensive user manual in printed form that was structured to emulate the look and feel of an actual vehicle owner's manual while being tailored for the experimental setup.",
    "The length of this user manual was around 1100 words.",
    "This manual consisted of three sections.",
    "The first section overviews the driving simulator's interface, layout, and operations.",
    "The second section offered detailed descriptions of all five ADAS functions' functionality and activation/deactivation processes, extending beyond the three discussed in the video."
